# Polymarket US API (api.polymarket.us) — CFTC-regulated.
# Generate an Ed25519 API keypair at polymarket.us/developer.
# Two values, both single-line. The secret is shown ONCE and cannot be recovered.
#   - Key ID:     a UUID
#   - Secret Key: a Base64-encoded Ed25519 private key
# Auth: headers X-PM-Access-Key / X-PM-Timestamp(ms) / X-PM-Signature,
#       signing the string "{timestamp}{method}{path}" with the secret key.
# Phases 1-3 are read-only (public market data) and need no credentials.
POLYMARKET_KEY_ID=
POLYMARKET_SECRET_KEY=
